---
---

<section id="features" class="section features-section">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<span class="section-subtitle text-gold">Pourquoi Mibeko ?</span>
			<h2 class="section-title text-navy">L'innovation légale au bout des doigts</h2>
			<p class="section-desc text-gray">
				Une plateforme pensée pour résoudre les défis quotidiens des professionnels et citoyens congolais grâce à une technologie de pointe.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="features-grid">
			<!-- Feature 1 -->
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon bg-navy">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-gold"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"></path><path d="m13 11-2-2"></path><path d="m11 13-2-2"></path></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="feature-title">Recherche IA Intelligente</h3>
				<p class="feature-text text-gray">
					Ne cherchez plus par mots-clés exacts. Posez votre question naturellement, notre intelligence artificielle comprend le contexte juridique et trouve les articles pertinents instantanément grâce à la recherche sémantique.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 2 -->
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon bg-navy">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-gold"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path><line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"></line></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="feature-title">100% Hors-ligne</h3>
				<p class="feature-text text-gray">
					Accédez à l'intégralité des textes de loi même sans connexion internet. Idéal pour les audiences au tribunal, les déplacements en province ou les zones à faible couverture réseau.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 3 -->
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon bg-navy">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-gold"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"></path><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"></path><circle cx="18" cy="4" r="3" fill="#D4AF37" stroke="none"></circle></svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="feature-title">Alertes en Temps Réel</h3>
				<p class="feature-text text-gray">
					Soyez le premier informé des nouvelles promulgations, décrets et jurisprudences. Recevez des notifications personnalisées pour rester constamment à jour sur l'évolution du droit congolais.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.features-section {
		background-color: var(--color-white);
		position: relative;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
	}

	.section-subtitle {
		display: block;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.section-desc {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2.5rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		background-color: var(--color-gray-light);
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 16px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.feature-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 4px;
		background-color: var(--color-gold);
		transform: scaleX(0);
		transform-origin: left;
		transition: transform 0.4s ease;
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-white);
		border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.08);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.feature-card:hover::before {
		transform: scaleX(1);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		border-radius: 14px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.15);
	}

	.feature-title {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-navy);
	}

	.feature-text {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 992px) {
		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
